And it can't occur on the last pixel of a scanline (x=255).<br /><br />But it can occur if the sprite and background are drawn with colors whose palette entries are the same (e.g. black) or if the sprite is drawn behind the background.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=9">tepples</a> — Sun Sep 04, 2005 11:27 am</p><hr />
